{"sn35.228:0.1":"Samyutta Nikaya 35.228 ","sn35.228:0.2":"18. Samuddavagga ","sn35.228:0.3":"Pathamasamuddasutta ","sn35.228:1.1":"“‘Samuddo, samuddo’ti, bhikkhave, assutava puthujjano bhasati. ","sn35.228:1.2":"Neso, bhikkhave, ariyassa vinaye samuddo. ","sn35.228:1.3":"Maha eso, bhikkhave, udakarasi mahaudakannavo. ","sn35.228:1.4":"Cakkhu, bhikkhave, purisassa samuddo; ","sn35.228:1.5":"tassa rupamayo vego. ","sn35.228:2.1":"Yo tam rupamayam vegam sahati, ayam vuccati, bhikkhave, atari cakkhusamuddam saumim savattam sagaham sarakkhasam; ","sn35.228:2.2":"tinno parangato thale titthati brahmano …pe… ","sn35.228:2.3":"jivha, bhikkhave, purisassa samuddo; ","sn35.228:2.4":"tassa rasamayo vego. ","sn35.228:2.5":"Yo tam rasamayam vegam sahati, ayam vuccati, bhikkhave, atari jivhasamuddam saumim savattam sagaham sarakkhasam; ","sn35.228:2.6":"tinno parangato thale titthati brahmano …pe… ","sn35.228:2.7":"mano, bhikkhave, purisassa samuddo; ","sn35.228:2.8":"tassa dhammamayo vego. ","sn35.228:2.9":"Yo tam dhammamayam vegam sahati, ayam vuccati, bhikkhave, atari manosamuddam saumim savattam sagaham sarakkhasam; ","sn35.228:2.10":"tinno parangato thale titthati brahmano”ti. ","sn35.228:2.11":"Idamavoca …pe… ","sn35.228:2.12":"sattha: ","sn35.228:3.1":"“Yo imam samuddam sagaham sarakkhasam, ","sn35.228:3.2":"Saumim savattam sabhayam duttaram accatari; ","sn35.228:3.3":"Sa vedagu vusitabrahmacariyo, ","sn35.228:3.4":"Lokantagu paragatoti vuccati”ti. ","sn35.228:3.5":"Pathamam. "}